beer.beer_name: Wax On Wax Off - Maku X Deep Creek
beer.beer_description: Wax on Wax Off Hazy IPA (6.5%) is  A Trans-Tasman collab between Maku Brewing & Deep Creek.  Like Sensei & Pupil working together to find Balance & Harmony taking inspiration from Deep Creeks Misty Miyagi & Maku’s Hemp infusion. together we have created something unique, a big fresh Hemp Hazy IPA bursting with passionfruit & Mango with the added complexity of Hemp.  Wax on Wax Off
